    <item>
      <title>欧洲央行行长帕内塔警告称低通胀风险需要进一步降息</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-31/ecb-s-panetta-warns-low-inflation-risks-require-more-rate-cuts</link>
      <description><![CDATA[欧洲央行管理委员会成员法比奥·帕内塔表示，欧洲央行必须继续降低借贷成本，以防止通胀率过低。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-31/ecb-s-panetta-warns-low-inflation-risks-require-more-rate-cuts</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 31 Oct 2024 09:50:10 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>里夫斯预算案出台后，英国债券市场仍处于紧张状态，债券价格下跌</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-31/uk-bonds-fall-with-market-still-on-edge-after-reeves-budget</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于市场预期未来几年新政府将实施大规模借贷和财政刺激计划，英国将实施更紧缩的货币政策，英国债券价格因此下跌。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-31/uk-bonds-fall-with-market-still-on-edge-after-reeves-budget</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 31 Oct 2024 08:58:54 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>韩国金融监管机构将调查韩国锌业的股票出售计划</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-31/korea-financial-watchdog-to-probe-korea-zinc-s-share-sale-plan</link>
      <description><![CDATA[韩国金融监管机构计划审查韩国锌业公司股票出售计划中可能存在的不当行为，称该案件“极有可能”构成不公平交易。]]></description>
